snippet.title: Smashbox Arena - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://smashboxarena.com
https://twitter.com/BigBoxVR

Smashbox Arena is a team-based online action game with insane physics-driven power-ups. 

Easy to learn, difficult to master -- Fast-paced, multiplayer designed from ground up for VR headset and touch controllers!
